{
  "texts": [
    "The encoder can process both forward and backward text flows simultaneously, while the decoder is used for auto-regressive generation of text sequences.",
    "Additionally, BART employs pre-training tasks such as masked language modelling and denoising auto-encoding to enhance model performance.",
    "Through pre-training, BART can learn universal language representations that can be fine-tuned for specific NLP tasks.",
    "BART has performed excellently in multiple NLP tasks and is widely used in various natural language processing applications.",
    "Section 5.1 explores applying different BART-based methods to the ACOSQE task based on the ACOS-Dataset, as shown in Table 8, and Sect. 5.2 summarizes this approach."
  ]
}